				<td colspan="2"><span>Can I whine about idiotic whines about whining? Or about mods abusing their power to suppress opinions they don't agree with?
<br />

<br />
Seriously, I've seen a ton of great and very helpful information out of you, and appreciate everything you do for this site.  That being said, the AE nerf was a big deal that affects a lot of bards in a big way.  People are going to talk about it.  A lot of people think it should be altered and/or repealed.  And are going to talk about it. Rightly so, as this is a general bard forum.  To say that bards can't discuss or express their opinion on the biggest change to their class in months makes absolutely no sense.
<br />

<br />
People that liked to AE kite want to let the devs know how unhappy they are about the nerf, and this is one of the best ways to do so.   Is it annoying? It gets that way very quickly, but you do a disservice to every member of this community by not allowing it.</span></td>
